urns can be generated by exploiting ‘investment anomalies’ or disruptive events believed to cause temporary undervaluation and that signal future outperformance knightsbridge places emphasis on absolute returns and invests opportunistically without regard to index characteristics at times they may use cash as a defensive tool portfolio holdings are diversified across marketcapitalization stocks are purchased only when knightsbridge believes an 8 to  investment return is probable over a three year holding period website httpwwwknightsbcom in the news see more see full news coverage and complete stories with relsci professional create your news feed see more executives  employees john gilbert prichard cofounder teresa ann wagner chief operating officer chief compliance officer  finance  accounting miles ellis yourman principal portfolio manager chad h neault research manager  research analyst see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to knightsbridge asset management llc knightsbridge asset management llc you connections via relationship science knightsbridge asset management llc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with knightsbridge asset management llc start my free trial ➤ see more holdings  top positions restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ knightsbridge asset management llc  newport beach california knightsbridge asset management llc phone    email knightsbridgeknightsbcom home philosophy investing professionals quarterly commenta